&quot;The best way to find yourself is to lose yourself in the service of others&quot;- Mahatma Gandhi<br>
<br>
NSS-IITM continues on its mission to be at the service of humanity with a new year of activities. We commence the events and projects for the year with the Inauguration Ceremony to be conducted on<br>
<strong>20th August 2016</strong>, Saturday at <strong>11:00 am</strong> in <strong>
Central Lecture Theatre</strong> <strong>(CLT)</strong>, IITM.<br>
<br>
<strong>Ms Aruna Roy</strong> has consented to be the chief guest at the function. Former IAS officer and Magsaysay award recipient, Ms Aruna Roy is an RTI activist and founder of the Mazdoor Kisan Shakti Sangathan.<br>
<br>
We cordially invite you all to the Inaugural Ceremony.<br>
<br>
PS:This is Credited event for all NSS Confirmed Volunteers and Defaulters.<br>
